		"description": "<p>The head of this magic maul is shaped like an adamantine fist. You gain a +2 bonus to <span class=\"freelinking-link\">attack and damage rolls</span>&nbsp;made with this weapon. When you hit an object or construct while wielding&nbsp;<em>Doorbreaker</em>, the hit is treated as a critical hit.</p>\n<p><em>Doorbreaker&nbsp;</em>has 3 charges. When you attack or touch a portal sealed with an&nbsp;<em><span class=\"freelinking-link\">arcane lock</span>&nbsp;</em>, you can expend 1 charge to cast&nbsp;<em><span class=\"freelinking-link\">@UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.z74pzb0a9lrha8qr]{Knock}</span></em><em>&nbsp;</em>on the portal.&nbsp;<em>Doorbreaker&nbsp;</em>regains 1d3 charges each dawn.</p>",
